1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
<i>Legend of Fei</i>

16
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:07,940
<i>Episode 14</i>

17
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,680
Let’s get some rest here.

18
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,870
Once Dragon Master and the troops leave,

19
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:15,190
we can get out and escape.

20
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,210
Escape?

21
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,800
Dragon Master is onto you.

22
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:21,800
Don’t even dream about escaping.

23
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,310
Dragon Master will hunt you down

24
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:25,060
no matter where you are.

25
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:27,760
You think this crappy hideout

26
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,340
can keep him away? Don’t be ridiculous!

27
00:02:30,870 --> 00:02:32,040
Aren’t you his follower?

28
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,120
Wouldn’t he save you?

29
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,550
If he arrives,

30
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:36,850
I’ll be his first target of murder.

31
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:41,900
Others take in disciples

32
00:02:42,510 --> 00:02:44,730
while Dragon Master has adopted 18 kids.

33
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,880
I heard others call you “Young Master”.

34
00:02:47,830 --> 00:02:50,320
Don’t flatter me. I’m ashamed of it.

35
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,880
Don’t you know

36
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,480
even dogs

37
00:02:54,830 --> 00:02:55,800
have names, too?

38
00:02:56,830 --> 00:02:58,440
Each time we see him,

39
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,530
we can only speak in prostration.

40
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:04,270
He’s also

41
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,980
marked all of us.

42
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:10,080
Where’s your mark?

43
00:03:11,550 --> 00:03:13,830
Didn’t you see that big mark?

44
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:15,680
You should be ashamed.

45
00:03:17,390 --> 00:03:18,720
You can say that again.

46
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:20,050
Be that as it may,

47
00:03:20,550 --> 00:03:22,510
I’m the smartest and most obedient

48
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:23,830
people pleaser.

49
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:27,500
So he always takes me with him.

50
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,800
Old Dragon was too dull

51
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:35,690
to be anywhere near Master,

52
00:03:36,110 --> 00:03:39,030
so he could only swallow his pride

53
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,300
and suck up to me.

54
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,540
That’s why I took him

55
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,600
to take care of that old fart.

56
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:51,030
Supposedly,

57
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:52,680
it wouldn’t take him too long.

58
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,370
But we didn’t expect

59
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,740
the North Blade

60
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:58,710
had help.

61
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:00,710
You’re good!

62
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,760
You killed Old Dragon.

63
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,360
Were it before that I bullied others

64
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,750
and made mistakes,

65
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:15,420
I’d be whipped and let go.

66
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,040
But this time,

67
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:23,140
whipping alone wouldn’t be enough.

68
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:26,210
You’re going to get beaten up.

69
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:48,040
The South and North Blades
were the Top Two.

70
00:04:49,470 --> 00:04:51,350
Li Zheng was in the south

71
00:04:51,350 --> 00:04:52,820
while Guan Feng was in the north,
hence the titles.

72
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,800
Old Master Li was
well-connected.

73
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:57,920
He became

74
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,950
a household name

75
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:00,940
because of the Fortress
of the Forty-Eight.

76
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,440
On the contrary,

77
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,440
Mr. Guan, Guan Feng,

78
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,200
was less engaged

79
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,450
although he was ten years older.

80
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,280
There were stories
about him in the past,

81
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,950
but ever since that armed rebellion,

82
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,080
he never came to Central Plains again

83
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,130
and only existed in stories.

84
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:24,070
My mother once told me about them.

85
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,520
The South Blade was cold

86
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,970
as the snowstorm

87
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:33,980
while the North Blade
could cut off water.

88
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,610
The North Blade was fierce.

89
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,830
Yes, he was,

90
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,870
fierce and shameless.

91
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,640
At that time,

92
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,660
I believed I was skilled enough

93
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:51,260
to leave for Central Plains.

94
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,800
My master didn’t want me to,

95
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,170
but I thought he was timid

96
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:58,960
and old.

97
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:00,820
I didn’t listen to him.

98
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,680
Seeing that he couldn’t change my mind,

99
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:10,440
he told me over and over before I left

100
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:12,540
to always think twice.

101
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:14,820
He said,

102
00:06:15,830 --> 00:06:16,800
“look,

103
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,880
your blade

104
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:23,330
is similar to a farmer’s hoe

105
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,830
and an accountant’s abacus.

106
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:31,120
Both are to get things done,

107
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:33,510
not to gain fame and wealth.

108
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:37,530
Do not mistake it”.

109
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:42,090
How is a blade equal to
a hoe or an abacus?

110
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,780
I didn’t get it either,

111
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,920
so I ignored it.

112
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,490
I thought

113
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:52,390
a blade is a weapon.

114
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:54,990
It has a soul

115
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:58,390
that connects mine

116
00:06:58,390 --> 00:07:01,220
as if it were part of my body.

117
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:05,750
How could it be compared
with a lifeless tool?

118
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,900
After I arrived in Central Plains,

119
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,260
soon,

120
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:24,350
I made a name of myself

121
00:07:24,350 --> 00:07:26,600
by this blade.

122
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,940
I was proud

123
00:07:28,790 --> 00:07:29,700
and I planned

124
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,970
to start my own sect

125
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:35,670
to revitalize the North Blade.

126
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,030
Within six months,

127
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,110
I challenged seven masters

128
00:07:40,110 --> 00:07:41,790
and beat them all

129
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,190
until...

130
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,390
Soon after the North Blade,
Ji Yunchen, arrived,

131
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:51,920
he defeated seven masters in a row.

132
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,480
So far, he hasn’t lost once.

133
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,670
He’s really something!

134
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:56,830
He hasn’t challenged Mr. Yin.

135
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,920
You know what?

136
00:07:57,920 --> 00:08:01,270
His master holed up

137
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:03,390
far away from Central Plains for so long

138
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,070
because

139
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:05,970
he had lost to the Mountain Sword,
Yin Wenlan.

140
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,510
Obviously,

141
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:09,550
water cutting is nothing.

142
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:11,320
It doesn’t deserve to be
one of the two Blades

143
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:13,010
as the Snow-breaking Blade does.

144
00:08:14,110 --> 00:08:15,600
Those rumors can’t be trusted.

145
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,910
I agree.

146
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:20,300
Where are you going next, Mr. Yan?

147
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:22,080
Not sure yet.

148
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,510
Please enjoy.

149
00:08:25,510 --> 00:08:26,580
Please.

150
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:45,460
<i>Yin’s Mansion</i>

151
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,460
Sir,

152
00:08:52,830 --> 00:08:53,600
you’d better leave.

153
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,240
Yin Wenlan!

154
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,220
<i>Yin Wenlan, the Mountain Sword</i>

155
00:09:00,550 --> 00:09:01,940
Are you not up for the challenge?

156
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:03,580
Fine.

157
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:06,480
I’ll wait here for three days.

158
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,110
If you don’t come out,

159
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:09,590
I’ll tell the world

160
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:12,150
the Mountain Sword is
inferior to the North Blade.

161
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:15,880
Yin Wenlan!

162
00:09:22,670 --> 00:09:24,590
When my mother was about my age,

163
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:26,520
she broke into Demons Manor

164
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:28,200
and battled the top three Demons

165
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,700
together with Duan Jiuniang.

166
00:09:30,470 --> 00:09:32,590
The latter was well-known for her Palm

167
00:09:32,590 --> 00:09:35,140
in her early 20s.

168
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,670
And Mr. Ji

169
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,940
quickly made a name of himself,

170
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:43,550
planning to set up his own sect.

171
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:46,100
But what about me?

172
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,060
What’s on your mind?

173
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,520
I think

174
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:55,880
my weapon is no different

175
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,080
from a blunt tool.

176
00:10:00,590 --> 00:10:02,080
Mr. Ji,

177
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,910
then what happened?

178
00:10:10,220 --> 00:10:16,300
<i>Yin’s Mansion</i>

179
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,820
What are you doing here?

180
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:24,080
Beat it, kid.

181
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,770
I’m not any kid.

182
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:28,520
The Mountain Sword,

183
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,120
Yin Wenlan, is my father.

184
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,660
You’re Yin Wenlan’s son?

185
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:35,350
Good. Go home

186
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:36,110
and tell your father to come out.

187
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:36,840
No.

188
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,760
Why?

189
00:10:37,760 --> 00:10:39,080
I sneaked out

190
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,430
because I didn’t want to study.

191
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:43,670
What do you want to do?

192
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:44,360
Play games.

193
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,450
Alright.

194
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,280
Let’s go

195
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,210
play games.

196
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,760
Once you have enough fun,

197
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,930
I’ll bring you back.

198
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,150
Alright?

199
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,350
This will be

200
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,630
our secret.

201
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:02,200
Let’s go.

202
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:03,960
That day,

203
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:07,640
Guan Feng charged at
Mr. Yin with his blade.

204
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,760
The two fought for 300 rounds.

205
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:10,870
Everyone,

206
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:15,060
can you imagine that?

207
00:11:15,790 --> 00:11:17,590
They fought so hard

208
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:21,000
that the world seemed to
fall apart in darkness.

209
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:26,080
All that could be seen
were gleaming blades.

210
00:11:26,710 --> 00:11:28,790
Still, Mr. Yin’s skills

211
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:32,560
were unparalleled, one of a kind.

212
00:11:33,350 --> 00:11:34,720
The Mountain Sword

213
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:36,180
crushed the North Blade

214
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:38,080
who lost terribly

215
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,990
and made a fool of himself.

216
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:43,030
-Yes! Great!
-Good!

217
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:44,110
Sir,

218
00:11:44,110 --> 00:11:45,640
who’s the North Blade

219
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:48,150
that lost terribly to my father?

220
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:51,280
I can’t wait to see that loser.

221
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:54,000
Everyone, that coward Guan Feng

222
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:57,400
was so scared of Mr. Yin...

223
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,180
What are you doing?

224
00:11:58,180 --> 00:11:59,400
That he...

225
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:00,550
What are you doing?

226
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:02,320
-Wet his pants.
-I want to hear more!

227
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,910
And he shivered in his sleep.

228
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:06,400
Hadn’t I heard

229
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,830
the made-up story,

230
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,800
I wouldn’t have lost control of myself.

231
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,040
You lost control

232
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:19,020
so you held that boy hostage

233
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,970
to force his father to battle you.

234
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:30,140
<i>Shanchan Temple</i>

235
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:55,570
Father.

236
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:01,850
Are you that boy?

237
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:06,620
Master,

238
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,000
bad news!

239
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:27,340
<i>Your son Yin Pei is in my hands...</i>

240
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:29,020
<i>Ji Yunchen</i>

241
00:13:35,110 --> 00:13:36,170
Bring me the sword.

242
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:37,550
Yes.

243
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:41,090
My father could destroy you

244
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:43,880
even if he was injured.

245
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:51,920
That’s right.

246
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,670
I wasn’t his match.

247
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:25,830
Mr. Ji,

248
00:14:26,470 --> 00:14:27,590
I didn’t expect

249
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:29,960
you’d go so low

250
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,800
just to challenge me.

251
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,390
My master’s reputation can’t be ruined.

252
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:35,840
Today,

253
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:39,080
I’m here to defend the North Blade.

254
00:15:31,350 --> 00:15:33,910
I didn’t know until later

255
00:15:33,910 --> 00:15:35,580
that he just drove those Demons away

256
00:15:36,550 --> 00:15:39,230
before I picked a fight.

257
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:40,720
He was already injured

258
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:43,110
but had to come

259
00:15:43,110 --> 00:15:44,670
under my threat.

260
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:45,930
When we fought,

261
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:49,100
he could’ve killed me.

262
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:57,400
I’d accept

263
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,960
whatever the result was.

264
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,470
I could start over

265
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:01,960
in ten years.

266
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:03,760
But

267
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:06,280
by breaking your sword,

268
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:08,260
you’re insulting me!

269
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,850
Mr. Ji,

270
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,220
you’ll have to go through thick and thin

271
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:17,560
in the years to come.

272
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:20,500
I simply don’t want

273
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:22,410
young men like you

274
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:24,980
to die in my hands for nothing.

275
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:28,300
Master, Master!

276
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,520
Help!

277
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:31,840
We’re under attack!

278
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,590
What?

279
00:16:32,590 --> 00:16:34,230
While you lured my father out,

280
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:35,460
those monsters broke in

281
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,640
and slaughtered my whole family!

282
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,000
A hundred of them

283
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,600
were killed!

284
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,690
Why are you still alive?

285
00:16:45,110 --> 00:16:47,350
Why aren’t you dead?

286
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,260
