577
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:24,710
I can only bluff like Xie Yun.

578
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:30,000
You’re a Guardian, huh?

579
00:34:32,160 --> 00:34:33,880
I bet

580
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:35,400
even Mu Xiaoqiao is better than you.

581
00:34:37,560 --> 00:34:38,770
Who are you?

582
00:34:41,950 --> 00:34:42,760
Take a guess.

583
00:34:44,160 --> 00:34:47,340
I guess you’re about to meet your doom!

584
00:34:54,830 --> 00:34:55,830
Watch it!

585
00:34:55,830 --> 00:34:57,800
I can cut off the heavenly river.

586
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:59,640
Don’t blink.

587
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:20,470
Seize her!

588
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,800
A one-on-one with Dragon Master?

589
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:36,000
What were you thinking?

590
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,840
Didn’t you pull me up?

591
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:41,150
Hadn’t it been for his palm,

592
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:42,100
you wouldn’t have

593
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:45,000
had such strength.

594
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:48,910
Should I thank him for that?

595
00:35:50,390 --> 00:35:52,180
My skills have improved a lot.

596
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,520
Stop laughing!

597
00:36:03,950 --> 00:36:06,050
As odd as he seems,

598
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,830
I still trust him for no reason.

599
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:13,120
Is it because of his look?

600
00:36:18,190 --> 00:36:19,950
Are you messing with me?

601
00:36:19,950 --> 00:36:22,040
Wait after we get out of here.

602
00:36:32,080 --> 00:36:33,390
What are you looking for?

603
00:36:34,910 --> 00:36:36,330
The secret tunnel should be nearby.

604
00:36:36,870 --> 00:36:38,370
It’s concealed though.

605
00:36:41,360 --> 00:36:43,630
Fei! Fei!

606
00:36:45,950 --> 00:36:46,760
Come here!

607
00:37:25,150 --> 00:37:26,390
Should I call you bold or stupid?

608
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:30,950
Where’s your blade?

609
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,360
None of your own business.

610
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:39,950
You fought against Dragon Master
barehanded.

611
00:37:39,950 --> 00:37:40,600
That’s...

612
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,000
I’ve got nothing

613
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,520
other than this.

614
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:49,470
Make do with it.

615
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,560
Where did you get this?

616
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,760
Is it to brace yourself up?

617
00:37:54,430 --> 00:37:55,870
I found it just now.

618
00:37:57,630 --> 00:37:58,950
You can think up

619
00:37:58,950 --> 00:37:59,800
all kinds of ways

620
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,600
to mock your own people.

621
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:03,390
But when it comes to

622
00:38:03,390 --> 00:38:04,950
life and death,

623
00:38:04,950 --> 00:38:06,190
you can only talk with your fists.

624
00:38:06,190 --> 00:38:08,190
Can you think first next time?

625
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:12,040
-You... You...
-Fei.

626
00:38:12,040 --> 00:38:13,320
Stop arguing.

627
00:38:14,430 --> 00:38:17,000
Don’t act rashly again.

628
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:18,280
But...

629
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:20,150
We’re worried about you.

630
00:38:20,150 --> 00:38:20,910
I...

631
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:22,430
Isn’t he safe and sound?

632
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:23,870
So am I.

633
00:38:23,870 --> 00:38:26,760
Yes, you returned intact,

634
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:29,630
but not your blade.

635
00:38:33,230 --> 00:38:34,390
Once I’m back,

636
00:38:34,390 --> 00:38:36,840
I’ll make you a bag

637
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:41,230
with multiple pouches around

638
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:42,360
for blades.

639
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,080
You can carry it

640
00:38:44,080 --> 00:38:45,800
like a peacock spreading its tail.

641
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,450
How nice and convenient that is!

642
00:38:48,230 --> 00:38:49,630
You won’t be short of weapons again.

643
00:38:52,470 --> 00:38:53,630
Where are you going?

644
00:38:58,870 --> 00:38:59,500
I’m going to...

645
00:39:04,230 --> 00:39:05,870
to... The Fortress
of the Forty-Eight with you.

646
00:39:09,870 --> 00:39:11,150
Let’s go.

647
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:13,840
Come on, Fei.

648
00:39:38,430 --> 00:39:40,120
There are signs of struggle.

649
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:47,520
Dragon Master must be badly injured.

650
00:39:47,520 --> 00:39:48,920
We can rest inside for now

651
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:50,840
until he leaves.

652
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:07,800
Is this the Forbidden Hall
of the Qi School?

653
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,890
Go get some clean water.

654
00:40:13,320 --> 00:40:14,090
What for?

655
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:16,020
You don’t need to know.

