00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:04,680
with water.

661
00:41:05,910 --> 00:41:06,720
Impressive!

662
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:09,080
Follow me.

663
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,390
-Miss Zhou. Miss Wu.
-Mr. Ji.

664
00:41:25,390 --> 00:41:26,360
And Xiao...

665
00:41:26,910 --> 00:41:29,320
I lied to them.

666
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,440
Call me Xie Yun.

667
00:41:31,670 --> 00:41:32,870
Mr. Xie,

668
00:41:32,870 --> 00:41:35,000
what is it about the Mountain Sword

669
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:35,780
that you told Dragon Master?

670
00:41:36,560 --> 00:41:37,990
He probably made that up.

671
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,470
Sorry.

672
00:41:44,470 --> 00:41:46,670
I lied to him.

673
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:51,080
But I did hear things

674
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:52,930
that might or might not be true.

675
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:54,370
What do you know?

676
00:41:56,230 --> 00:41:57,520
It’s said that

677
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:59,520
when the South Blade
was hunted by Demons,

678
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,870
he fought and ran

679
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:05,650
but was almost caught more than once.

680
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:07,690
Then unexpectedly,

681
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:12,170
he destroyed his weapon.

682
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,760
Is that true?

683
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:20,980
Why did I hear nothing from my father?

684
00:42:22,710 --> 00:42:24,150
I don’t

685
00:42:24,150 --> 00:42:25,790
get that, either.

686
00:42:26,910 --> 00:42:27,560
Think about it.

687
00:42:28,040 --> 00:42:29,190
When someone is

688
00:42:29,190 --> 00:42:30,330
after you,

689
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:32,360
will you destroy your weapon

690
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:35,190
instead of trying to escape?

691
00:42:35,190 --> 00:42:36,240
Of course not.

692
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:41,070
Then those blabbermouths

693
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:44,110
spread rumors

694
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:46,360
about some evil magic

695
00:42:46,360 --> 00:42:48,190
that as long as

696
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:50,630
one obtained a master’s weapon,

697
00:42:50,630 --> 00:42:53,150
he could gain that person’s skills.

698
00:42:57,320 --> 00:42:59,040
That’s bullcrap.

699
00:42:59,040 --> 00:43:00,440
Utter nonsense.

700
00:43:01,710 --> 00:43:03,910
Mr. Ji is unsuspecting.

701
00:43:03,910 --> 00:43:05,060
He seems to be convinced.

702
00:43:06,950 --> 00:43:08,520
Don’t look at me, Mr. Ji.

703
00:43:08,520 --> 00:43:10,000
That’s just what I heard.

704
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:11,800
But I did learn to cast swords

705
00:43:11,800 --> 00:43:13,300
to dig deep into it.

706
00:43:14,950 --> 00:43:16,490
How could that be possible?

707
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,790
It’s baseless.

708
00:43:19,150 --> 00:43:20,710
Are you saying

709
00:43:20,710 --> 00:43:23,130
Dragon Master plotted
against Mr. Yin Wenlan

710
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:26,110
because of such hogwash?

711
00:43:27,230 --> 00:43:28,040
About that,

712
00:43:28,710 --> 00:43:30,660
you need to ask Mr. Yin.

713
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:48,560
Mr. Yin.

714
00:43:54,390 --> 00:43:55,950
Now, can you tell us

715
00:43:55,950 --> 00:43:57,700
why Dragon Master insists on
having you back?

716
00:44:10,040 --> 00:44:11,100
It makes sense

717
00:44:11,560 --> 00:44:14,050
that you fell out
with your foster father

718
00:44:14,320 --> 00:44:16,630
after knowing the truth

719
00:44:16,630 --> 00:44:17,540
about your family’s murder.

720
00:44:18,430 --> 00:44:19,840
What doesn’t make sense is

721
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:21,280
you’d come all the way

722
00:44:21,630 --> 00:44:23,070
to kill a feeble man

723
00:44:23,950 --> 00:44:25,760
at the cost of exposing yourself

724
00:44:25,760 --> 00:44:27,100
after enduring years of humiliation.

725
00:44:29,390 --> 00:44:31,710
He seemed to come to stir up trouble

726
00:44:31,710 --> 00:44:33,560
with Old Dragon,

727
00:44:33,560 --> 00:44:36,470
but actually, he wanted Old Dragon dead.

728
00:44:38,560 --> 00:44:41,120
When he pretended to kill others

729
00:44:41,710 --> 00:44:43,190
but got stopped

730
00:44:43,190 --> 00:44:44,720
by your chopstick,

731
00:44:45,360 --> 00:44:46,340
he didn’t leave

732
00:44:47,000 --> 00:44:49,110
but went straight into the Sanchun Inn

733
00:44:49,320 --> 00:44:50,720
and came at you.

734
00:44:51,320 --> 00:44:52,760
He was picking a fight on purpose.

735
00:44:52,760 --> 00:44:53,160
Exactly.

736
00:44:54,670 --> 00:44:55,950
Then, of course,

737
00:44:55,950 --> 00:44:57,710
you caught him.

738
00:44:58,360 --> 00:44:59,950
Other than that,

739
00:44:59,950 --> 00:45:01,350
he kept fanning the flames

740
00:45:02,150 --> 00:45:03,350
to incite you to kill Old Dragon.

741
00:45:03,800 --> 00:45:05,080
No wonder

742
00:45:05,080 --> 00:45:06,590
he’s been clinging on to us

743
00:45:06,910 --> 00:45:08,000
without any attempt to escape.

744
00:45:09,080 --> 00:45:10,420
Later, when Dragon Master arrived

745
00:45:10,760 --> 00:45:11,980
and encountered Wen Yu,

746
00:45:12,360 --> 00:45:14,000
he managed to get out

747
00:45:16,320 --> 00:45:17,960
and planned to kidnap Miss Wu.

748
00:45:19,150 --> 00:45:20,020
That way,

749
00:45:20,560 --> 00:45:22,020
he could take advantage
of Wen Yu’s power.

750
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:23,990
Although he failed,

751
00:45:24,470 --> 00:45:25,630
he still got out

752
00:45:25,630 --> 00:45:26,680
with us.

753
00:45:29,600 --> 00:45:30,430
Miss Zhou.

754
00:45:33,630 --> 00:45:35,670
You’re smart enough
to figure out everything.

755
00:45:35,670 --> 00:45:37,360
Why are you asking me?

756
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:39,360
I’m not half

757
00:45:39,360 --> 00:45:40,950
as smart and calculative as you are.

758
00:45:43,190 --> 00:45:44,840
He can’t fight anymore.

759
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:45,950
What if

760
00:45:45,950 --> 00:45:48,040
no one in the Inn could stop Old Dragon?

761
00:45:48,040 --> 00:45:48,870
Did that ever occur to you?

762
00:45:53,430 --> 00:45:54,720
Not everyone

763
00:45:55,040 --> 00:45:56,810
is as lucky as you, lass!

764
00:45:57,560 --> 00:46:00,260
You have family support and fine skills.

765
00:46:01,080 --> 00:46:02,080
You’re so spoiled

766
00:46:02,080 --> 00:46:04,040
and ignorant.

767
00:46:04,840 --> 00:46:05,840
Is that

768
00:46:05,840 --> 00:46:08,320
a complaint or a compliment?

769
00:46:09,230 --> 00:46:11,000
Without Ji Yunchen,

770
00:46:11,000 --> 00:46:13,080
I would’ve become the heir

771
00:46:13,080 --> 00:46:14,330
to the Mountain Sword.

772
00:46:15,190 --> 00:46:17,470
You wouldn’t even get to lick my boots!

773
00:46:17,470 --> 00:46:18,190
What did you say?

774
00:46:18,190 --> 00:46:19,320
You heard me!

775
00:46:19,760 --> 00:46:20,130
You...

776
00:46:21,910 --> 00:46:23,450
Don’t mind it.

777
00:46:28,600 --> 00:46:30,120
Yes, what could’ve happened?

778
00:46:30,950 --> 00:46:33,080
The worst case would be Ji Yunchen

779
00:46:33,080 --> 00:46:34,710
and some unlucky man

780
00:46:34,710 --> 00:46:36,870
died in Old Dragon’s hands.

781
00:46:36,870 --> 00:46:38,180
What was that to do with us?

782
00:46:38,840 --> 00:46:41,370
So you could easily tell him

783
00:46:41,710 --> 00:46:43,140
that Ji Yunchen was your enemy.

784
00:46:43,670 --> 00:46:45,120
That wouldn’t raise any suspicion

785
00:46:45,120 --> 00:46:46,560
as the good and the evil

786
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:47,910
were born to be foes.

787
00:46:47,910 --> 00:46:49,800
Old Dragon wouldn’t suspect a thing.

788
00:46:49,800 --> 00:46:51,670
If he killed Ji Yunchen,

789
00:46:51,670 --> 00:46:53,580
that’d only boost his ego.

790
00:46:54,000 --> 00:46:55,410
Because never did he know

791
00:46:55,600 --> 00:46:56,480
that you’re a Yin,

792
00:46:56,800 --> 00:46:57,850
nor would he ever expect

793
00:46:58,230 --> 00:46:59,320
that you wouldn’t

794
00:46:59,710 --> 00:47:01,310
go back after this.

795
00:47:09,110 --> 00:47:12,620
♪Stars flow like river♪

796
00:47:13,680 --> 00:47:17,280
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

797
00:47:17,850 --> 00:47:21,920
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

798
00:47:22,170 --> 00:47:25,810
♪I will never be alone♪

799
00:47:25,810 --> 00:47:29,930
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

800
00:47:30,350 --> 00:47:34,780
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

801
00:47:35,440 --> 00:47:40,000
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

802
00:47:40,230 --> 00:47:44,860
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

803
00:47:45,050 --> 00:47:48,880
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

804
00:47:49,100 --> 00:47:53,790
♪When I go across the world for you♪

805
00:47:54,050 --> 00:47:57,790
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

806
00:47:58,120 --> 00:48:03,210
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

807
00:48:03,210 --> 00:48:07,150
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

808
00:48:07,150 --> 00:48:11,680
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

809
00:48:12,300 --> 00:48:19,400
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

810
00:48:20,140 --> 00:48:24,770
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

